#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ", and feel free to"
msgstr "お気軽に"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Create a new opportunity"
msgstr "1. 新規案件を作成する"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Book an appointment"
msgstr "2. 予約する"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Verify your schedule"
msgstr "3. スケジュールを確認する"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. Take notes during your appointment"
msgstr "4. 予約中にメモを取る"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "5. Check your invoices"
msgstr "5. 顧客請求書を確認する"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Appointments App</b>: Offer seamless online booking for consultations and "
"sessions, allowing clients to schedule\n"
"                time with you 24/7."
msgstr ""
"<b>アポイントメントアプリ</b>:相談やセッションのオンライン予約をスムーズに受"
"け付け、クライアントは24時間いつでも\n"
"                自分で予定を予約できます。"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Calendar App</b>: Manage your daily schedule efficiently, avoiding double "
"bookings and ensuring you have adequate\n"
"                preparation time between clients."
msgstr ""
"<b>カレンダーアプリ</b>: 日々の予定を効率よく管理し、予約の重複を防ぎ、クライ"
"アントの間に\n"
"                十分な準備時間を確保できます。"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Contacts App</b>: Maintain a clean and organized directory of all your "
"clients, suppliers, and professional\n"
"                partners."
msgstr ""
"<b>連絡先アプリ</b>: すべての顧客、サプライヤー、およびビジネス\n"
"                パートナーの情報を、整理整頓されたディレクトリで管理します。"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Invoicing App</b>: Simplify your finances by generating professional "
"invoices for sessions and packages, ensuring\n"
"                you get paid on time."
msgstr ""
"<b>請求アプリ</b>: セッションやパッケージの請求書をプロ仕様の形式で作成し、支"
"払いの遅延を防いで期日どおりに\n"
"                入金できるようにします。"

